column1: # The observer, Mr Newbitt lived at 19 Royal Crescent.
# The gauge moved, most likely to Chubb Hill Gardens, in 1909.
# The readings for April-December 1904, 1905, 1906 and 1907 are estimates and have been omitted.
# The sheet is shared with the Chubb Hill Gardens site - the readings for 1908 and 1909 are for Chubb Hill Gardens.
